atest/20181218/644311?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181218%2F644311%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=tGK3uc%2BiZyPMDkLrkWE6i9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=25332677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181218%2F644311%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=fe94a1df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181218/644311?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n去年曾接受本刊訪問的90後美女礦工Macy再次接受訪問，直言現時大家都知道掘礦難賺錢，坦言現時都沒有靠砌礦機及掘礦賺錢；而是做回老本行，做programmer。她坦言礦機生意最賺錢都是頭半年，其後都已經改為研究區塊鏈技術而非砌礦機作主要收入。現時不會再稱自己為礦工，她已有另一個「計劃」，全情專注於區塊鏈技術，與友人以區塊鏈技術大搞交友app，望發展另一條路。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"出次新聞 呃完班水魚就轉行<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}